<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīramaṇu(ṁ) ḍartthi <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ṁḍu voṟaṁḍūrivibhuṁḍu gaśyapagōtrōddhāru(ṁ)ḍanaṁ bara
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ge nīlasarasīruhasaṁbhbhavakuluṁ<unclear>ḍu</unclear> śivadēvu(ṁ)ḍananu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> [Ā]tanikiṁ buṇyamūrttiki nātataguṇanidhi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ki guṁḍamāṁbaku dharmmōpē<unclear>tu</unclear>(ṁ)ḍu satyanityanikētanuṁ<unclear>ḍai</unclear> puṭṭe maṁtrikēta(ṁ)ḍu vērmmini <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Atani
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ki(ṁ) brītu(ṁ)ḍai muddamāṁbaku(ṁ) buṭṭe namātyavidda(ṁ) ḍūrjitanayaśāli yītaniki siṁdhuragāmini dōnamā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṁbakunu hitamitabhāṣi gēta(ṁ) ḍudiyiṁcce samastajanānurāgu(ṁ)ḍai śa<unclear>ta</unclear>makhabhōgi vāni Anujanmu(ṁ)ḍu
<lb n="6"/>viddanamalla(ṁ)ḍunnatini <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśakavarṣamulu<note n="67-1">Thelu is cut below the line.</note>1073 gunēṁṭi Uttarāyanasaṁkrāṁtti nimittamuna śrīmanmahā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>maṁḍalēśvara tribhuvanamalladēva pottappi<unclear>cōḍa</unclear>mahārājula <unclear>rājā</unclear>dhyakṣa viddanapeggaḍa koḍku mallayapeggaḍa
<lb n="8"/>kammanāṁṭilōni prēṁpalli śrībhāvanārāyaṇadēvara kācaṁdrārkka makhaṁḍavartti dīpamunakuṁ beṭṭina biru
<lb n="9" break="no"/>dumāḍalu <unclear>12</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vīniṁ jēkoni māreni kāmarāju koḍuku dēvana tana putrānupauvitrikamu nitya māne
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁḍu neyi pōyaṁgalavāṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

